{"tid":2269132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北韓逾萬人接受病毒篩檢病例數仍為零","createTime":"2020-11-03T09:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:59:29.000Z","uid":310867,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e65bf9ffdb7280eda2deaf236ff54597dc7bfc6c","tid":2269132,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織（WHO）公布報告指，北韓已對超過一萬人進行病毒篩檢，而檢測結果全部呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n根據韓聯社報導，世界衛生組織3日公布報告，截至10月22日，北韓已對1萬462人檢測，截至10月29日，接受檢測的人都未出現確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n目前為止，北韓境內有5368起疑似病例，其中8例是外國人士。10月15日至22日間，北韓有161人接受隔離，累計隔離人數達3萬2011人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201103/DAYHTAFW6FF5PKS57TJQMIGFME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201103%2FDAYHTAFW6FF5PKS57TJQMIGFME%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVboxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=1001c9b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201103%2FDAYHTAFW6FF5PKS57TJQMIGFME%2F&h=d3b276fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201103/DAYHTAFW6FF5PKS57TJQMIGFME/</a>"},{"pid":"6b698fee16e334b15b7872142d8db2f78bfaec29","tid":2269132,"uid":310867,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"北韓防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1234dda2995b05f7264fc8ac0e89b32324af4398","tid":2269132,"uid":310867,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"英國廣播公司報道，北韓中央電視台（KCTV）日前播出特別天氣預報，警告將有一陣來自中國的「黃沙」湧入，更聲稱可能會帶有武漢肺炎病毒，呼籲民眾留在室內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201024/6SQ4EO5IO5HJXG3SDAM7LJX26Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201024%2F6SQ4EO5IO5HJXG3SDAM7LJX26Y%2F&d=A